---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import WellnessQuote from '../components/WellnessQuote.astro';
import BreathingSpace from '../components/BreathingSpace.astro';
import NaturalCTA from '../components/NaturalCTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Philosophy"
  description="Discover our holistic approach to cat care. We believe in natural harmony, sanctuary living, and mindful choices that nurture both you and your feline companion."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-mist to-cream breathing-space text-center">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-sage mb-4 block">Our Philosophy</span>
      <h1 class="text-display text-earth mb-6">
        Living in Natural Harmony
      </h1>
      <p class="text-body text-earth-light max-w-xl mx-auto leading-generous">
        We believe that wellness flows from the choices we make each day‚Äîchoices that honor
        our bodies, our homes, and the creatures who share our lives.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Philosophy Content -->
  <section class="container-narrow py-16">
    <article class="prose max-w-none">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-earth mb-6">The Sanctuary Mindset</h2>
      <p class="text-body text-earth-light mb-6 leading-generous">
        Your home is more than a place to live‚Äîit's a sanctuary where you restore, reconnect,
        and nurture the most important relationships in your life. When we approach our living
        spaces with this mindset, every choice becomes an opportunity for intention.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body text-earth-light mb-6 leading-generous">
        The products we bring into our homes carry energy. Some add to our sense of peace;
        others subtract from it. Conventional cat litters‚Äîwith their synthetic fragrances,
        chemical dust, and artificial additives‚Äîwork against the harmony we seek to create.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body text-earth-light mb-8 leading-generous">
        Natural alternatives, by contrast, work <em>with</em> us. They support our intention
        to live cleanly, simply, and in alignment with the rhythms of nature.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <BreathingSpace size="sm" withLine withIcon icon="‚ùÄ" />

  <!-- Three Pillars -->
  <section class="container-wide py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-heading text-earth mb-4">Three Pillars of Mindful Cat Care</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Pillar 1 -->
      <div class="card-organic text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-sage/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <span class="text-4xl">üåø</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-earth mb-4">Natural Ingredients</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-earth-light leading-generous">
          We honor what comes from the earth. Corn, wheat, pine, walnut, coconut‚Äîthese
          materials have nourished life for millennia. In our cat's litter box, they
          continue that legacy of gentle, effective care.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 2 -->
      <div class="card-organic text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-terracotta/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <span class="text-4xl">üïäÔ∏è</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-earth mb-4">Gentle Effectiveness</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-earth-light leading-generous">
          Powerful doesn't mean harsh. Nature has perfected odor control through millions
          of years of evolution. Activated carbon, plant fibers, and natural enzymes
          work quietly but profoundly to maintain freshness.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 3 -->
      <div class="card-organic text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <span class="text-4xl">‚ôªÔ∏è</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-earth mb-4">Sustainable Cycles</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-earth-light leading-generous">
          What we use returns to the earth. Biodegradable materials complete nature's
          cycle, leaving no lasting footprint. This is caring that extends beyond
          our homes to the world we share.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <BreathingSpace size="md" />

  <!-- Quote Section -->
  <section class="bg-sand/30 py-16">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <WellnessQuote
        quote="When we care for our cats with intention, we practice a form of meditation. Each scoop, each cleaning, each choice becomes an opportunity to be present and mindful."
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <BreathingSpace size="md" />

  <!-- Cat as Teacher -->
  <section class="container-narrow py-16">
    <article class="prose max-w-none">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-earth mb-6">Your Cat as Wellness Guide</h2>
      <p class="text-body text-earth-light mb-6 leading-generous">
        Cats are masters of presence. They don't worry about yesterday or tomorrow‚Äîthey
        live fully in the now. When we observe them, we're reminded of what true relaxation
        looks like, what authentic comfort feels like.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body text-earth-light mb-6 leading-generous">
        This presence makes cats remarkably sensitive to their environment. They notice
        when something feels "off." They respond to the energy of products, spaces, and
        the people around them. A cat who avoids their litter box may be telling us
        something important about what we've placed in their most intimate space.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body text-earth-light mb-8 leading-generous">
        By choosing natural litter, we listen to this wisdom. We create an environment
        where our cats can be fully themselves‚Äîwhere their instincts are honored rather
        than overridden.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <BreathingSpace size="sm" withLine withIcon icon="‚ú¶" />

  <!-- Purrify Section -->
  <section class="container-wide py-16">
    <NaturalCTA
      title="Aligned with Our Philosophy"
      description="Purrify represents everything we believe in‚Äînatural coconut-derived activated carbon that works in harmony with your chosen litter. No artificial fragrances, no harsh chemicals, just pure, effective odor elimination."
      ctaText="Explore Purrify"
      ctaHref="https://purrify.ca/learn/how-it-works?utm_source=allnaturalcatlitter&utm_medium=philosophy"
      variant="earth"
      external={true}
    />
  </section>

  <BreathingSpace size="lg" />

  <!-- CTA to Natural Path -->
  <section class="container-narrow text-center pb-20">
    <h2 class="text-heading text-earth mb-4">Continue Your Journey</h2>
    <p class="text-body text-earth-light max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8">
      Explore our collection of mindful guides to natural cat litter and holistic living.
    </p>
    <a href="/the-natural-path" class="btn-primary">
      Discover The Natural Path
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
